pageProduct.name: Swisse Men's Ultivite 50+ Multivitamin 90 Tablets
pageProduct.description:
General Information

Swisse Ultivite Men's 50+ Multivitamin is a premium quality formula containing 41 vitamins, minerals, antioxidants and herbs to support a healthy, active lifestyle. Tailored for men 50 years and over, this comprehensive multivitamin supports energy production, stamina, cognitive function and healthy immune function.

Size: 90 Tablets

Warnings

The recommended daily amount of vitamin A from all sources is 700 mcg/RE for women and 900 mcg/RE for men.

Vitamin & mineral supplements should not replace a balanced diet.

If symptoms persist consult your healthcare practitioner.

Do not take while on warfarin therapy without medical advice.

This product contains selenium which is toxic in high doses. A daily dose of 150 micrograms for adults of selenium from dietary
supplements should not be exceeded.

Ingredients

Biotin 200 mcg; Folic acid 500 mcg; Nicotinamide 25 mg; Vitamin A (retinol acetate) 750 mcg RE; Vitamin B1 (thiamine hydrochloride) 35 mg; Vitamin B2 (riboflavin) 35 mg; Vitamin B5 (pantothenic acid from calcium pantothenate) 68.7 mg; Vitamin B6 (pyridoxine from pyridoxine hydrochloride) 20.56 mg; Vitamin B12 (cyanocobalamin) 120 mcg; Vitamin C (ascorbic acid from calcium ascorbate dihydrate) 165.30 mg; Vitamin D3 (cholecalciferol) 5 mcg; Vitamin E (d-alpha-tocopheryl acid succinate) 25 mg; Vitamin K (phytomenadione) 70 mcg; Calcium (from calcium orotate) 10 mg; Chromium (from chromium picolinate) 50 mcg; Copper (from copper gluconate) 1.7 mg; Iodine (from potassium iodide) 150 mcg; Iron (from ferrous fumarate) 5 mg; Magnesium (from magnesium aspartate dihydrate) 7.5 mg; Manganese (from manganese amino acid chelate) 4 mg; Molybdenum (from molybdenum trioxide) 45 mcg; Selenium (from selenomethionine) 26 mcg; Zinc (from zinc amino acid chelate) 20 mg; Citrus bioflavonoids extract 20 mg; Co-enzyme Q10 (ubidecarenone) 3 mg; Lutein 1 mg; Soy Phosphatidylserine-Enriched Soy Lecithin Powder Containing soy phosphatidylserine 2 mg 10 mg; Spearmint oil 2 mg; Cranberry (Vaccinium macrocarpon extract 10 mg) equiv. dry fruit 1 g; Bilberry (Vaccinium myrtillus extract 1 mg) equiv. fresh fruit 100 mg; Grape Seed (Vitis vinifera extract 8.33 mg) equiv. dry seed 1 g; Ginkgo (Ginkgo biloba extract 20 mg) equiv. dry leaf 1 g; Globe Artichoke (Cynara scolymus extract 500 mcg) equiv. dry leaf 50 mg; Hawthorn (Crataegus monogyna extract 1.2 mg) equiv. dry fruit 120 mg; Liriosma Ovata (Dulacia inopiflora extract 2 mg) equiv. dry root 200 mg; Milk Thistle (Silybum marianum extract 24.29 mg) equiv. dry fruit 1.7 g; Nettle (Urtica dioica extract 500 mcg) equiv. dry leaf 50 mg; Saw Palmetto (Serenoa repens extract 3 mg) equiv. dry fruit 300 mg; Skullcap (Scutellaria lateriflora extract 500 mcg) equiv. dry herb 50 mg; Tribulus (Tribulus terrestris extract 10 mg) equiv. dry fruit 500 mg; Tribulus (Tribulus terrestris extract 10 mg) equiv. dry root 500 mg.

Directions

DIRECTIONS FOR USE - ADULT DOSAGE:
WARNING: If you are pregnant, or considering becoming pregnant, do not take vitamin A supplements without consulting your doctor or pharmacist. When taken in excess of 3000 mcg/RE, vitamin A can cause birth defects.
One tablet daily, during or immediately after a meal, or as directed by a healthcare professional.

STORAGE INSTRUCTIONS

Store below 25°C in a cool, dry place.
